:0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T17:53:00.000Z","msg":"不如比我地救翻你出嚟<br />\n等我地一齊再行落去 再一齊去煲底慶祝"},{"pid":"285c8a78032b01b81f666b3d04e0454355da8fd9","tid":2019994,"uid":189021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T17:53:40.000Z","msg":"手足 不如pm我傾下？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c62eaea1904b125d30203d79ee2bbc8747273e8","tid":2019994,"uid":203702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T17:53:53.000Z","msg":"手足咩事，我知依家好多分化<br />\n但正正係鍛鍊我地嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51089eddbb9b3c19f50eb320646d78eda5d6f60","tid":2019994,"uid":69999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T17:56:26.000Z","msg":"你係香港人 就同我哋一齊加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9881e4f9fbf7ea3e0c0986c81417917d91aa9d55","tid":2019994,"uid":186294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T17:56:46.000Z","msg":"唔係話會一齊見咩？<br />\n台灣民主化都打左40年<br />\n但佢地都贏左<br />\n香港人醒目咁多實會快過佢地<br />\n冇左你唔得wo"},{"pid":"8f52592ef8fe8290268a57fbed5576b08f8d43fc","tid":2019994,"uid":186294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T17:57:39.000Z","msg":"我地好多人都好攰，但都會互相扶持陪伴，一齊行埋落去"},{"pid":"9dcf82fec14d8153dcf5cb57920d7be11b2cf1d4","tid":2019994,"uid":189021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"285c8a78032b01b81f666b3d04e0454355da8fd9","tid":2019994,"uid":189021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T17:53:40.000Z","msg":"手足 不如pm我傾下？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T17:57:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99daa8e5dece78aeb6a69a6347e43eac3c52aa90","tid":2019994,"uid":186294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T17:59:06.000Z","msg":"雖然我地素未謀面<br />\n但你想打波食黃店煲劇飲湯嗎？<br />\n我可以陪你架..."},{"pid":"7bd05ceb6eff95f28ac72f7e265623c702cde1dc","tid":2019994,"uid":346970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T17:59:39.000Z","msg":"無論其他人點講都好<br />\n明白你嘅人會明白你<br />\n自己骨子裏嘅信念冇人可以偷得走<br />\n其他人點講都唔會改變到你嘅思想<br />\n你喺呢一場運動出咗嘅力<br />\n<br />\n我知其他人嘅閒言緋語你令好辛苦<br />\n但佢哋咁唔明白你<br />\n用言語去攻擊你<br />\n證明佢哋根本唔熟識你<br />\n所以唔需要咁重視佢哋講嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n不如咁吖<br />\n聽下一啲開心啲嘅歌<br />\n食下朱古力、糖<br />\n咁樣會令心情好返啲㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋一個都不能少<br />\n唔想等我哋贏嗰陣你睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n同壞人鬥長命"},{"pid":"6ebf872ed84e23bf3769393f4dadcd920ac37178","tid":2019994,"uid":82452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T18:02:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要煲底見呀"},{"pid":"189bab2c434158468218b5ec36c3a3105ffc6e92","tid":2019994,"uid":233968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T18:05:02.000Z","msg":"手足你應下我地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d684125ae808dbc6877a99c0e39579b80e4e45","tid":2019994,"uid":21385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T18:05:44.000Z","msg":"只有生存先會有希望"},{"pid":"2a11355fd30056efc9553827c05fdb7415aa7b3f","tid":2019994,"uid":240004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T18:06:41.000Z","msg":"一直覺得罐頭正能量說話好膠好廢話<br />\n但到今年想鼓勵安慰手足 原來真係諗唔出咩說話可以講<br />\n<br />\n煲底見可能聽到厭 但希望你明白大家係真心想同你行落去 唔係得閒飲茶之類"},{"pid":"2df724ae749921d9366bf8c7fc937104f8ecbc78","tid":2019994,"uid":261731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T18:10:24.000Z","msg":"你應該知道我哋都好需要你㗎<br />\n如果你都當我哋係手足<br />\n大家撐住大家行落去啦好嘛？<br />\n香港人人加油唔可以少左你果份<br />\n記得我哋上年6月講過<br />\n「多你一個真係好多！」<br />\n我哋約好左同好多好多手足煲底見㗎"},{"pid":"dcc470f3d55a88e0fb849795718d2d0f0ddf2e6b","tid":2019994,"uid":72094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T18:11:25.000Z","msg":"撐住呀手足<br />\n應承咗一齊撐落去<br />\n我仲要喺煲底見你架！！"},{"pid":"da224b98a1f0256d1351bd6734f10e062a68c27c","tid":2019994,"uid":233968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T18:13:32.000Z","msg":"我地冇咗邊個都唔得嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咩事我撐你好冇？"},{"pid":"abd680d35b86ae5390b06ee5bcc8e5c24b3f497f","tid":2019994,"uid":261731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T18:16:36.000Z","msg":"我知道唔係講一句「加油、撐落去」<br />\n生活就會變得好正能量<br />\n我本身都係好憎正能量撚嘅<br />\n不過無左條命就真係真正乜都做唔到<br />\n所以我會留住條命<br />\n一路行一路睇下有乜做到<br />\n應下我哋啦樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e583a70e095b76cdb12c8cdd197de771790c992","tid":2019994,"uid":318129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T18:16:41.000Z","msg":"對唔住手足<br />\ndietoy<br />\n最終<br />\n我都係想你去孭起<br />\n至少<br />\n你呢一世都唔會唔記得呢一幕<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8WCzizj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8WCzizj.png&h=96716298&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bdf28ddcecb8561267764101b7a1c908828547a","tid":2019994,"uid":72094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T18:16:42.000Z","msg":"唔好有事呀手足<br />\n頂住<br />\n我地一齊撐住"},{"pid":"254e943a73dd71fb930f0695068f6b33e0a20b73","tid":2019994,"uid":240004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T18:20:11.000Z","msg":"等我哋搵你食宵夜"},{"pid":"b527da445d42aaaa56b17afa57413e066d05e4c0","tid":2019994,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T18:21:41.000Z","msg":"手足我地係到啊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />攰就休息下 等我地努力<br />\n有咩唔開心同我地講好冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09a4b3551b832fd1a4026b97f39682832f31507","tid":2019994,"uid":37959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e583a70e095b76cdb12c8cdd197de771790c992","tid":2019994,"uid":31812