5-16T18:59:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/egkzQioUVjw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FegkzQioUVjw&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=843977f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/egkzQioUVjw</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇睇過呢條片？<br />\n佢都係狗仔狗女<br />\n但佢係我地珍視既手足<br />\n<br />\n只要你理念同我地一樣<br />\n你就係手足"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:05:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07307293f0700611f0e0a75a6220d5f7e47eee5","tid":2019994,"uid":219969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:12:26.000Z","msg":"樓主，明白有情緒病真係好辛苦<br />\n但我哋一齊行落去呀，呢啲好多手足都好關心好緊張你<br />\n我哋要一齊煲底攬攬㗎<br />\n同我哋傾吓啦！"},{"pid":"7d5696f16b8c7325689a7a0200f6a42ba816bc37","tid":2019994,"uid":240004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:12:54.000Z","msg":"樓豬唔好做傻事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfff6b24dffb78943853fd8c916b5042e7ef53a7","tid":2019994,"uid":219969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:15:52.000Z","msg":"樓主你係咪仲睇緊呀？<br />\n知你一定係好大好大壓力<br />\n但用死證明一啲野真係唔值得<br />\n留低傾吓啦，好多對耳仔喺度"},{"pid":"418ba64195949ece7e1049ea26b017a3bdf64f3c","tid":2019994,"uid":154223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:16:38.000Z","msg":"你點可以咁自私自己走咗去？呢度好多人同你一樣經歷無數個無眠夜，無數個淚流披面嘅晚上。我哋好多人都同你一樣咁冇力，點解你就可以咁自私自己走咗去，dum低我哋？ <br />\n<br />\n你知唔知每次我哋見到手足離開個心情有幾低落？心中團火唔係比呢個政權淋熄，喺身邊一個個手足離我地而去而淋熄。<br />\n<br />\n對唔住我哋冇辦法為你行落去，我地只能夠一齊行落去。<br />\n<br />\n唔好走"},{"pid":"621ecc556eee51bef6eacde42fd4bc1c9157b0bd","tid":2019994,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:18:23.000Z","msg":"我知你已經捱左好耐<br />\n所以你真係好叻㗎啦（攬攬樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc39cac78f31fc9170d14357c3919323c220e41","tid":2019994,"uid":304411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:18:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"404c35b800ee7dd307f4674dd7579980692a7789","tid":2019994,"uid":219969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:19:21.000Z","msg":"手足撐住呀！！！<br />\n海邊好凍，俾個hug你，行開冷靜下先好唔好？"},{"pid":"6068baa63fbee36c624808d592ec9564976d6267","tid":2019994,"uid":219969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2f74b51e03ff6a86a87c5addf96170d43560f84a","tid":2019994,"uid":240004,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T18:53:31.000Z","msg":"樓豬 有個傻仔半夜飛錯的去錯尖沙咀<br />\n睇在佢份上唔好做傻事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u4XSPT0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu4XSPT0.png&h=4963b4cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:21:57.000Z","msg":"樓主睇吓手足幾錫你！（雖然好柒）<br />\n快啲笑鳩佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92cb39cbe8809ef03179a198cd4f5b0c159194c","tid":2019994,"uid":71524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:28:23.000Z","msg":"老細～<br />\n講黎聽下啦<br />\n手足同你搵方法拆掂佢啦"},{"pid":"7e55a113d53eb6b792badeb43f9eb7c17149f4fd","tid":2019994,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:35:33.000Z","msg":"手足我地係哂度架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ce21c017b0dc32cf822da482d59e272db8eeed","tid":2019994,"uid":240004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:41:05.000Z","msg":"好多手足搵緊樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65bb8f43af267962998c3a673d751f34a7862355","tid":2019994,"uid":357341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:42:37.000Z","msg":"有冇人搵到？"},{"pid":"130f05d0dc7512f9ddd3e099163203190957d81a","tid":2019994,"uid":307882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:43:17.000Z","msg":"一方有難八方支援<br />\n手足有咩需要相信都有人幫到你<br />\n只要你肯講就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果想自己靜吓都交低聲啦<br />\n等其他手足放心啲嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夜晚吹咁耐風好易冷親㗎 嚟緊成個禮拜都落雨添啊 小心唔好病啊好嗎？"},{"pid":"d23f0c4d35e4245ee4d0ff44e3ce2e9b5f759767","tid":2019994,"uid":262817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:43:54.000Z","msg":"樓主快啲番屋企啦 夜喇危險呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e5f140831b04fc5ca499f335745bffe2db04c5","tid":2019994,"uid":10684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:45:11.000Z","msg":"快啲返屋企啦 落雨啦"},{"pid":"17f3e2b1b8e857bc4ab0ca43a8cd4f80197bf46c","tid":2019994,"uid":240004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T20:04:10.000Z","msg":"樓豬放下水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6875e8b53cd58df7e3a91c637792dd21d1756064","tid":2019994,"uid":224490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T20:08:31.000Z","msg":"我想訓美容覺啊，樓主過黎一齊好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69e54936cbcaf9769a2d9af212164810313cde28","tid":2019994,"uid":254028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T20:22:27.000Z","msg":"上水啦樓主 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fcc5d64220c48599afa98cfd5281825e1aa387a","tid":2019994,"uid":271248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T20:25:48.000Z","msg":"樓主叫大家比啲爭扎但就忍心拋低我地咩？<br />\n上水啦樓主<br />\n等緊你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579533cd8bf2895947dc71543b0c025d79755e76","tid":2019994,"uid":205356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T20:29:31.000Z","msg":"發生左咩事？可唔可以講多小小？"},{"pid":"dfa8ba08831d133ac3bc81e9b79ce89aff5a29ae","tid":2019994,"ui